item.title: Resume
item.description: Passionate software engineer with 4+ years of experience building web applications utilized by over 9000 K12 admins, teachers, and students. Streamlined many aspects of managing an e-commerce platform, allowing staff members to focus on empowering K12 CS educators instead of wrestling with systems. Built a cyber range portal from scratch that allows hundreds of students to participate in cybersecurity exercises in a safe environment. Eager to work on exciting projects and learn new tools and skills along the way.
